tment research and a high level of customer service our roster of clients has grown over the years but these basic beliefs remain unchanged we are value investors in constructing portfolios for the oakmark funds and other clients we seek out businesses that we believe are priced at significant discounts to their underlying value these companies must offer significant profit potential and be run by managers who think and act as owners we frame the investment process as owning a piece of a business for the long term we believe in the importance of intensive fundamental research our experienced investment analysts evaluate each company on the basis of its fundamental characteristics our research process is based on a disciplined quantitative and qualitative screening process we recognize that each of our clients has unique goals and needs therefore portfolios are crafted to meet those objectives we are as proud of our client service as we are of our outstanding longterm investment results assets under management at harris associates totaled approximately  billion as of june   our team includes  investment professionals and  total employees harris associates is an autonomous subsidiary of natixis global asset management lp for more information on separate accounts and subadvisory services managed by harris associates please visit wwwharrisassoccom learn more about employment opportunities at harris associates account access click here for secure login open a new account online navs for investoradvisorinstitutionalfundnavchgytdoakmarkoakmxselectoaklxequity  incoakbxglobaloakgxglbl selectoakwxinternationaloakixintl sm capoakexfundnavchgytdoakmarkoaymxselectoaylxequity  incoaybxglobaloaygxglbl selectoaywxinternationaloayixintl sm capoayexfundnavchgytdoakmarkoanmxselectoanlxequity  incoanbxglobaloangxglbl selectoanwxinternationaloanixintl sm capoanex i want to open an account make an account transaction request a prospectus download literature view fund performance get answ